---
import AdminLayout from '../../layouts/AdminLayout.astro';
---

<AdminLayout title="Dev Notes CMS | 影像档案" active="watch" dataAttr="data-watch-admin">
  <input slot="search" class="cms-search" type="search" placeholder="搜索影像名、评论、佳句..." data-watch-search />
  <a slot="actions" href="/#watch" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">预览影像区</a>

  <Fragment slot="sidebar-actions">
    <span>快速操作</span>
    <button type="button" data-create-watch>新增影像</button>
    <button type="button" data-filter="missing_image">扫描缺图</button>
    <button type="button" data-filter="missing_comment">扫描缺影评</button>
    <button type="button" data-filter="missing_quote">扫描缺佳句</button>
  </Fragment>

  <div class="cms-hero">
    <div>
      <span>Archive Health</span>
      <h1>影像内容控制台</h1>
      <p>写评论、填佳句、上传影像图。保存后前台即时生效，不需要SSH到服务器改文件。</p>
    </div>
    <strong data-save-state>ONLINE / DB CONNECTED</strong>
  </div>

  <div class="cms-metrics" data-watch-stats></div>
  <div class="cms-filters">
    <button type="button" data-filter="all" class="active">全部</button>
    <button type="button" data-filter="missing_image">缺图</button>
    <button type="button" data-filter="missing_comment">缺影评</button>
    <button type="button" data-filter="missing_quote">缺佳句</button>
    <button type="button" data-filter="watched">已看</button>
    <button type="button" data-filter="wanted">想看</button>
    <button type="button" data-filter="watching">在看</button>
    <button type="button" data-filter="activity">观看近况</button>
    <button type="button" data-filter="featured">精选</button>
  </div>
  <div class="cms-list" data-watch-list></div>

  <aside slot="editor" class="cms-editor" data-watch-editor>
    <p>从左侧选择一个影像条目开始编辑。</p>
  </aside>

  <script is:inline src="/admin-watch.js"></script>
</AdminLayout>
